---
title: Hearty Meatball and Mushroom Stew with Roasted Garlic Parmesan Mash
description: Meatball and mushroom stew is kind of like the food equivalent of a well-worn, fuzzy sweater – comforting, familiar and warm. It’s a timeless dish that never goes out of fashion!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-de-boulettes-et-de-champignons-b502fdaa.jpg
